page.title: 05TRANSPORT
page.content: Steven + Simon. When we started our project we thought about car's. A list of car's to see. ford. capri, fiesta, cortina, orion,. vauxhaull. cavalier, nova, opel, cresta, chevette. Mgt midget. mini.clubman, city, van, copper,. opel manta. avenger. granada. popular/ford. mazda. thats some of the car's that we found on the road. Ther are other forms of transport on the road like bike's motorbike's most people that are young ride moter,bike's.But some of them drive car's around the village and in fields
